Package: askLLM
Type: Package
Title: Ask LLM about your data
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Sau-Chin Chen <pmsp96@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Sau-Chin Chen <pmsp96@gmail.com>
Description: Ask a large language model questions about the dataset you
    have open in jamovi. Select the variables you care about and the module
    attaches their summary statistics (never the raw rows) to your question,
    so the answer is grounded in your data. Works with NVIDIA NIM, Google
    Gemini, GitHub Models, a local Ollama server, or any OpenAI-compatible
    endpoint. API keys are read from your environment and are never stored
    in the .omv file.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: jmvcore (>= 0.8.5), R6, ellmer, yaml
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0), withr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
